<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>A colorize effect renders the source with a tint of its color(). The color can be modified using the setColor() function.</db:para>
<db:para>By default, the color is light blue (<db:link xlink:href="qcolor.xml">QColor</db:link>(0, 0, 192)).</db:para>
