<db:section xml:id="QGraphicsColorizeEffect">
<db:title>QGraphicsColorizeEffect::QGraphicsColorizeEffect(QObject *<db:emphasis>parent</db:emphasis> = 0)</db:title>
<db:para>Constructs a new <db:link xlink:href="qgraphicscolorizeeffect.xml">QGraphicsColorizeEffect</db:link> instance. The <db:code role="parameter">parent</db:code> parameter is passed to <db:link xlink:href="qgraphicseffect.xml">QGraphicsEffect</db:link>'s constructor.</db:para>
